name: World's Deepest Eel
description:
The deepest true eel ever recorded from the scientists who took it. This is the never released unedited raw data as it came from the lander vehicle. The eel, likely Ilyophis robinsae, was recorded at 6,068 m/19,908 ft depth. To date, this is the only observation of an anguilliform at hadal depths - i.e., greater than 6,000 m/19,685 ft deep.

Discovery
https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0967063716300656
World record
https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/626705-deepest-eel

The verified owners of this NFT are entitled to ‘behind the scenes’ media about the find which has never been released. 
As well as the above, the first to purchase this NFT will be invited to an in-person experience to be arranged based on their geographical location.
